<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Pharmacy Registration Needs Approval</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #f39c12; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .footer { padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #3498db; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>New Pharmacy Registration</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello Admin,</h2>
            <p>A new pharmacy has registered and requires approval:</p>
            
            <p><strong>Pharmacy Name:</strong> <%= pharmacyName %></p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
            <p><strong>Business Phone:</strong> <%= businessPhone %></p>
            <p><strong>Registration Date:</strong> <%= registrationDate %></p>
            
            <p>Please review this registration in the admin panel:</p>
            
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= adminUrl %>" class="button">Review Registration</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2023 Recyleto Admin System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>